creator: Tiledmedia
descriptionHtml:
The highest quality 360º video streaming solution arrives on Android!

Immerse yourself in high high quality virtual environments at low bandwidth, based on our award winning ClearVR viewport adaptive video streaming technology.

Immerse yourself in Surround Vision's The Female Planet (https://surroundvision.co.uk/portfolio/female-planet-series-google/)
- A collection of 5 high-quality 360º films allowing the audience to shadow five extraordinary women with careers in science, technology, sports and the arts who share their personal and professional experiences.

Visit Paris (Footage by Digital Immersion, http://www.digitalimmersion.com):
- Notre-Dame de Paris area.

Watch live performance (Footage by Digital Immersion, http://www.digitalimmersion.com):
- Blue man group, Las Vegas.

See the other side of Formula 3 (Footage by Ericsson, https://www.ericsson.com):
- Jamie Chadwick's driving session

Note that you will need a reasonable Internet connection speed (10-20 Mbit/s) to view the videos in the best quality possible.
